export default class MapPolyfill {
  public size = 0;
  private _values = [];
  private _keys = [];
 
  get(key) {
    let i = this._keys.indexOf(key);
    return i === -1 ? undefined : this._values[i];
  }
 
  set(key, value) {
    let i = this._keys.indexOf(key);
    if (i === -1) {
      this._keys.push(key);
      this._values.push(value);
      this.size++;
    } else {
      this._values[i] = value;
    }
    return this;
  }
